window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Some cases don't stay buried.</b></p> <p>My name is Ethan Drake. I'm the cop who works the occult cases nobody else will touch the ones that reek of brimstone and old blood.</p> <p>My partner's a demon. My sanity runs on whiskey, cigarettes, and a drug called Mud.</p> <p>And the thing that slaughtered my wife and daughter is still out there.</p> <p>Now graves are being robbed, souls harvested, cults rising, and something ancient and starving is clawing its way into our world.</p> <p>Let them try.</p> <p>I've got a demon hunting me for my body, Internal Affairs gunning for my badge, a foul-mouthed Hellicorn with an attitude problem, and enough darkness in my soul to make whatever's coming wish it had stayed dead.</p> <p>The city doesn't know it yet, but I'm the only thing standing between humanity and extinction.</p> <p>Some days, I'm not sure which side I'm on.</p> <p>This complete first-arc box set contains all three full-length Ethan Drake novels:</p> <ul> <li><b>Infernal Justice</b></li> <li><b>Blood Summoned</b></li> <li><b>Death Dealers</b></li> </ul> <p>Expect hardboiled occult detective noir, demons, dark magic, and a burned-out hero who's already lost everything except his gun.</p> <p>Harry Bosch meets John Constantine. If you love Dresden Files, Sandman Slim, or The Iron Druid, clear your schedule.</p> <p><b><i>Download now and binge the entire first arc tonight.</i></b></p>"; 
